{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"41cc69cdc3","title":"大字报——无花蔷薇","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4416abdce6","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"41cc69cdc3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4e38dc5cec","name":"西北师范学院"},{"id":"6ffc5739af","name":"车轰"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3f5820c7c9","type":"title","text":"大字报——无花蔷薇","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"c9dc62a2c8","type":"authors","text":"西北师范学院车轰","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"1d1e7008f8","type":"paragraph","text":"有这样一小撮人；他们过去靠依附“三害”起家，现在又想靠替“三害”打“掩护战”发迹籍口某些“别有用心”的大字报的出现，梦想用“大帽子”压倒运动，好以后爬上高居群众之上的宝座。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"cda45f4887","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说这些人是“三害”的狗尾巴，我们说这不是狗尾巴，而是绵羊尾巴，因为狗尾巴还有根骨头。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"4f7a5024a3","type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"22852861d4","type":"paragraph","text":"“蚍蜉撼大树，可笑不自量”韩愈老先生早就这样嘲笑过了，然而今天仍有这种的可笑“蚍蜉”他们趁着这大放大鸣的阶段，把宗派和党派混为一谈，把我们今天的缺点夸张为“乌云天、漆黑地”他要想在党的身上抹灰，不小心却抹白了自己的鼻子。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"473669193e","type":"paragraph","text":"党是坚强的，永远推不倒的，党敢于放手发动大家大放大鸣，这就是党强大有力，相信自己的证据。“蚍蜉”们的技俩，其结果只有一个他引起了群众的警惕，它说明了阶级斗争还在进行。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"472c200a2c","type":"paragraph","text":"当然，“蚍蜉”们的乱鸣还产生了另一种效果：他们捣乱了群众的视线，无意之间给“三害”抵抗运动的挡箭牌。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"d720173645","type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"4f30234a20","type":"paragraph","text":"在中央统战部召开的会议上有人发言说积极份子是挖“沟”筑“墙”的义勇队，这种笼统的提法打伤了一些跟着共产党走的真正的积极份子，事实上又在那里筑“墙”。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"6e20069f01","type":"paragraph","text":"然而也还有这样一种头载浩然巾的“两面派的积极份子”，他们对党员胁肩谄笑，对群众耀武扬威，筑“墙”挖“沟”的工作就是他们担当了好多。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"fd750bea8d","type":"paragraph","text":"×　　×　　×","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"ce2fa77ba6","type":"paragraph","text":"宗派主义者爱骂别人是搞小集团，搞小圈子，因为要喝散了群众，他们的宗派主义才得以巩固。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"d726d11a0c","type":"paragraph","text":"眼睛明亮的人会发现，在某些指责别人搞小集团，小圈子的言论中就往往有宗派主义的蛛丝马迹可寻。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"705cf17199","type":"paragraph","text":"混战的阶段似乎过去了，混战中有些战术，却还使人记忆尤新，仅记录下来，供未来的“军事学家”研究：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"10c8a29ff5","type":"paragraph","text":"一曰：连骂带打，文武全才，但愿天下大乱，方好拍手称快；","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"bd412ff63f","type":"paragraph","text":"二曰：小事化大，跟着起哄，只顾要看热闹，管他后果如何；","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"9f64c8200d","type":"paragraph","text":"三曰：混淆是非，指鹿为马，不惜歪曲事实，但求打倒对手；","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"4aefe19436","type":"paragraph","text":"四曰：化名围攻，以壮声势，表面百家争鸣，其实仅此一家；","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"137cb7f027","type":"paragraph","text":"五曰：指桑骂槐，指东说西，表面嘻嘻哈哈背后悄悄捣鬼；","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"cff3fd408a","type":"paragraph","text":"六曰：冒名顶替，制造混乱，为求挑拨诬蔑，不惜违法乱纪；","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"94b2a86750","type":"paragraph","text":"七曰：帽子横飞，借装“纠偏”，搬用肃反武器，好使群众结活；","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"a0d5067432","type":"paragraph","text":"八曰：混水摸鱼，诬蔑全党，利用花言巧语，想使运动变质；","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"b31f53af85","type":"paragraph","text":"九曰：避重就轻，避大谈小，说话躲躲闪闪以便蒙混过关；","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"8f64c7f171","type":"paragraph","text":"十曰：趁机报复，攻击私人，不问运动方向，但求发泄私怨；稍有不信，请细看满校的各色大字报。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"f2b4179f1b","type":"paragraph","text":" ——车轰","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"},{"id":"9ebfb92f19","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《香花乎？毒草乎？(1)》（西北师范学院学委会，1957年6月18日）。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3"}],"page":{"id":"58db890009","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"41cc69cdc3","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}